          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-teal text-lg mb-2">What the Stars Engine Does</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed">The Stars Engine computes a complete birth chart from a client's birth date, time, and location using JPL ephemeris data — the same NASA-grade astronomical calculations used by professional astrologers. It determines exact planetary positions and computes <strong>128 distinct data layers</strong> spanning Western tropical, Vedic sidereal, Human Design, Gene Keys, Ba Zi, Mayan, cosmobiology midpoints, and more.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mt-3">A dedicated <strong>structural_integration</strong> computation module maps this architectural data onto the 10-session Rolfing protocol — translating planetary positions into fascial holding patterns, Gene Key shadows into body regions, and cosmobiology midpoints into structural friction warnings.</p>
          </div>
